{
  "texts": [
    "By analogy with SMC 2, we term the resulting algorithm nested EnKF (NEnKF).",
    "In what follows, we provide the basic NEnKF algorithm before considering some extensions for improving efficiency.",
    "The NEnKF recursively targets π enkf,t (θ, x 1:N t |y 0:t) which can be constructed by taking the extended target π enkf,t (θ, x1:N 0:t, x 1:N 0:t |y 0:t) ∝ π(θ) p",
    "and marginalising out x1:N 0:t and x 1:N 0:t-1.",
    "Hence, given a weighted parameter sample {θ i, u i t-1 } with associated ensemble x i,1:N t-1, i = 1,."
  ]
}